---
description: UX and accessibility rules for a calm, premium interface.
alwaysApply: true
globs: ["**/*.html","**/*.py"]
---

- Use NHS.UK design patterns; for MVP use semantic HTML, large tap targets, clear focus states, error summaries.
- Keep forms short with plain English; progressive disclosure; mobile-first.
- Add basic Pa11y/axe check scripts; server-rendered pages must be keyboard-navigable.
